articles.title: 'The Social Network' sequel will focus on Haugen leaks, with Jeremy Strong as Mark Zuckerberg - TechCrunch
articles.description: Fifteen years after "The Social Network," director Aaron Sorkin is making a sequel film about Facebook called "The Social Reckoning."
articles.content:
Fifteen years after “The Social Network,” Aaron Sorkin will write and direct a sequel film called “The Social Reckoning,” set for release on October 9, 2026.
